{
  "texts": [
    "The consumer side can be a frustrating and confusing place to be, given that it is occupied by both impassioned enthusiasts and ardent skeptics.",
    "Both are to a degree right.",
    "AI tools can be productively used in empirical research but only if they are housed inside an econometric framework that does not require unrealistic assumptions in either direction.",
    "This paper provides one such framework, resulting in meaningful contracts for using LLMs in empirical research.",
    "Provided those contracts are adhered to, our results suggest that LLMs can expand the scope of empirical research without compromising its rigor."
  ]
}